comments: Sexton (CLE) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (MIN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Drummond (CLE).
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Edwards (MIN) in transition.
Garland (CLE) makes marginal contact with Russell (MIN) during his drive.
Garland (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position on Okogie (MIN) during the drive.
Russell (MIN) and Nance Jr. (CLE) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Okogie's (MIN) arm.
Garland (CLE) and Vanderbilt (MIN) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Russell (MIN) makes marginal contact with Drummond (CLE) during the shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Garland (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position on Russell (MIN) and absorbs the contact.
Okoro (CLE) makes marginal contact with Beasley's (MIN) arm as he receives the pass.
Okoro (CLE) makes marginal contact with Beasley's (MIN) body after he releases the shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, a clear path foul is assessed to Drummond (CLE).
